data.title: Campus Sites
data.text:
Off-Campus Sites

A significant amount of the classes are located on the De Anza College campus. Carefully check the class meeting days, times, and room, and utilize the campus map to find the classroom. An "F" in the section number denotes that the course is at an off-campus site. Check the course notes for the class for details on the location.

Some of the off-campus sites are listed below. Please contact the division office if you are unsure where the location of your course is.
